Question: At least one panda is lying on its back.

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='How many pandas are lying on their back?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many pandas are lying on their back?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} + {ANSWER1} >= 1')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
